OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778674272
OL,3,CForced adoption scandal: 'I wasn't
OL,4,Cadopted because I was not white'
OL,6,FITV News has heard heartbreaking
OL,7,Ftestimony from survivors about the
OL,8,Fracism they endured, Social Affairs
OL,9,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker and Senior
OL,10,FProducer Lottie Kilraine report
OL,12,FBlack and mixed heritage adoptees and
OL,13,Fcare-leavers who faced "abhorrent"
OL,14,Fracism and prejudice during the forced
OL,15,Fadoption era want their lifelong
OL,16,Ftrauma and suffering to be
OL,17,Facknowledged by the church and state.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778674272
OL,3,CForced adoption scandal: 'I wasn't
OL,4,Cadopted because I was not white'
OL,6,FBetween 1949 and 1976 hundreds of
OL,7,Fthousands of unmarried mothers were
OL,8,Fforced to put their children up for
OL,9,Fadoption, simply because they were
OL,10,Funmarried.
OL,12,FMothers of mixed heritage children
OL,13,Fwere told they had no choice and their
OL,14,Fbabies would be "better off" adopted.
OL,16,FThe reality was that the adoption and
OL,17,Fcare system at that time deemed them
OL,18,Fas "un-adoptable" and "undesirable",
OL,19,Fmeaning many grew up in orphanages and
OL,20,Fchildren's home, suffering abuse and
OL,21,Fneglect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778674272
OL,3,CForced adoption scandal: 'I wasn't
OL,4,Cadopted because I was not white'
OL,6,FITV News has heard heartbreaking
OL,7,Ftestimony from survivors about the
OL,8,Fracism they endured, and how it has
OL,9,Faffected their whole lives.
OL,11,F'I wasn't adopted or fostered because
OL,12,FI was not white'
OL,14,FFrom the moment Phil Frampton was born
OL,15,Fin 1953, his care records show that he
OL,16,Fwas treated with prejudice and
OL,17,Fdiscrimination because of the colour
OL,18,Fof his skin, with racist language used
OL,19,Fthroughout.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778674272
OL,3,CForced adoption scandal: 'I wasn't
OL,4,Cadopted because I was not white'
OL,6,F"The reason I wasn't adopted or
OL,7,Ffostered was because I was not white,"
OL,8,Fhe told ITV News.
OL,10,F"When I was a baby the matron wrote:
OL,11,F'Philip is such a poor specimen of
OL,12,Fhumanity and there are doubts about
OL,13,Fhis intelligence'."
OL,15,FHis mother, Mavis Frampton, was one of
OL,16,Fhundreds of thousands of women who
OL,17,Fwere forced to put up their babies for
OL,18,Fadoption because they gave birth out
OL,19,Fof wedlock, the ultimate social taboo
OL,20,Fin post-war Britain.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778674272
OL,3,CForced adoption scandal: 'I wasn't
OL,4,Cadopted because I was not white'
OL,6,FShe had sought refuge at the Rosemundy
OL,7,FHome for Unmarried Mothers in St Agnes
OL,8,Fin Cornwall, which was linked to the
OL,9,FChurch of England, hundreds of miles
OL,10,Faway from her home in Birmingham.
OL,12,FInstead of help, she was told to pray
OL,13,Ffor forgiveness and labelled a fallen
OL,14,Fwoman.
OL,16,FDr Frampton told ITV News that his
OL,17,Ffather, who was Black and from
OL,18,FNigeria, was removed from the UK for
OL,19,Fdating his mother.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778674272
OL,3,CForced adoption scandal: 'I wasn't
OL,4,Cadopted because I was not white'
OL,6,FHe grew up in orphanages in the south
OL,7,Fwest of England and then later
OL,8,Fchildren's homes in the north west. At
OL,9,Fone point he was even sent to a home
OL,10,Ffor disabled children, despite having
OL,11,Fno disabilities.
OL,13,FHe was unaware of his own mother's
OL,14,Fexistence until the moment that, at 14-
OL,15,Fyears-old, he was told that she had
OL,16,Fdied.
OL,18,FParts of his childhood in care were
OL,19,F"brutal" and have shaped who he is
OL,20,Ftoday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778674272
OL,3,CForced adoption scandal: 'I wasn't
OL,4,Cadopted because I was not white'
OL,6,F"All I had was Black skin, black curly
OL,7,Fhair, and I was abused and called all-
OL,8,Fsorts," he said.
OL,10,F"How do you escape from that? You have
OL,11,Fto live in it. I grew up conscious of
OL,12,Fnot being a citizen of this country.
OL,14,F"This is not 200 years ago, this is in
OL,15,Four living memory. This is my life.
OL,16,FIt's easy to say move on, but this
OL,17,Fisn't the past, it's part of me."
OL,19,F'The assumption was that Black
OL,20,Fchildren could not be adopted'
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
