OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778674272
OL,3,CForced adoption scandal: 'I wasn't
OL,4,Cadopted because I was not white'
OL,6,FCardinal Vincent Nichols acknowledged
OL,7,F"the grief and pain caused by the
OL,8,Fgiving up of a child through
OL,9,Fadoption", and added that "the
OL,10,Fpractices of all adoption agencies
OL,11,Freflected the social values at the
OL,12,Ftime".
